{"tid":1926964,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［突發］意大利市長感染新冠肺炎病逝","createTime":"2020-03-15T12:56:17.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-15T13:16:32.000Z","uid":48124,"like":9,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"6448f046fbdf44a58b86617996490545878c9eb8","tid":1926964,"uid":48124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T12:56:17.000Z","msg":"意大利倫巴底區貝爾加莫（Bergamo）切內市（Cene）市長瓦洛帝（Giorgio Valoti）日前因感染新冠肺炎入院，13日病逝，成為該國首位因新冠肺炎病逝的地方首長。<br />\n<br />\n根據當地媒體報導，貝爾加莫政府在14日通報，70歲的瓦洛帝在幾天前確診，住進當地醫院後，12日病情開始惡化，送入重症加護病房急救後，仍在13日宣告不治，成為當地首名因新冠肺炎逝世的地方首長。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，瓦洛帝在意大利北部疫情爆發後，仍舊親自指揮各項防疫措施，在與居民頻繁的接觸之下，不幸染疫。義大利前副總理、極右派聯盟黨（Lega）領袖薩爾維尼（Matteo Salvini）也在推特放上兩人合照悼念，「感謝為這城市奉獻一生。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n原文：<a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/news/20200315/1668131.htm#ixzz6GlIuoTUX\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20200315%2F1668131.htm%23ixzz6GlIuoTUX&d=%2BoN05yFcfnwTDzsdE0HOyTvkInyplymEwWc8t9jwBTE%3D&h=3f5ffbf3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/news/20200315/1668131.htm#ixzz6GlIuoTUX</a>"},{"pid":"451ae2ce1484bbfd0d71b6ca0da30770a6656863","tid":1926964,"uid":268519,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T13:00:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TNVPH29.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTNVPH29.png&h=ed3fa0c5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1a0b1eb313b17c86d6c26fa70eb873c8f3cfef90","tid":1926964,"uid":58413,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T13:01:11.000Z","msg":"🇫🇷"},{"pid":"735416b310f532ebd354fb79aed06c90253614ef","tid":1926964,"uid":93649,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T13:01:54.000Z","msg":"2日...係意大利醫療廢定隻毒真係勁"},{"pid":"54cc055115186154e2fac1cc72c552694925d263","tid":1926964,"uid":176282,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-15T13:01:57.000Z","msg":"it&rsquo;s just a flu<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" c